Just make it easy.  Go into Ssra mines and kill the wussy named skeletons until you get a Dusty Soriz Worker Pouch.  Clicky summon Shissar Fangs.  The summon takes like 30 seconds and gets you one stack, but the fangs are NOT no rent, so you can stock up while waiting for KEI or something.
